{"tid":1645411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真假命題之光復後公務員架構提案","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T07:31:59.000Z","uid":131892,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52958855ee998eeec2d9d4c8b7700fba208705d6","tid":1645411,"uid":131892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"其實呃咗大家入黎之後我都無咩磚可以拋，但港共去到今時今日咁好大程度係因為佢哋自以為高市民一等，而市民永遠唔敢反抗。<br />\n所以光復後其中一件大家會唔會係削減公務員光環先，由人工福利著手，變得同市價睇齊。<br />\n一來可以畀返啲高學歷嘅人出市場<br />\n二來只有真係有心嘅人先會入政府<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f15c40878b542aa216ac05056d97db05a1010f","tid":1645411,"uid":71988,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"做得政府都是狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為中共工作"},{"pid":"5008d8c1cc85da23773eaa7eacdf0fa64b13b053","tid":1645411,"uid":40493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"WSD藍到仆街"},{"pid":"dc25f769f42edfa76f537db76370568ec67bbfc0","tid":1645411,"uid":131892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9f15c40878b542aa216ac05056d97db05a1010f","tid":1645411,"uid":71988,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"做得政府都是狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為中共工作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"對對<br />\n但光復後要點令佢哋真心為香港人呢<br />\n我大膽估計<br />\n依家班人當初係為錢入政府做<br />\n所以當中國畀更大利益佢時，佢哋就會衝"},{"pid":"69b04338f84acd4e2298b13380acea3e6e664bcc","tid":1645411,"uid":131892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5008d8c1cc85da23773eaa7eacdf0fa64b13b053","tid":1645411,"uid":40493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"WSD藍到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"水務署？？？<br />\n應該大部份都藍，因為佢哋睇利益，而中國剝削大家後畀到利益佢哋"},{"pid":"110ef0cd287cb75da0b4291c588eb2073413a4da","tid":1645411